  <brief_title>A Study to Assess the Efficacy of Gefapixant (AF-219/MK-7264), a P2X3 Receptor Antagonist, in Subjects With Chronic Cough</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Study to Assess the Efficacy of AF-219, a P2X3 Receptor Antagonist, in Subjects With Chronic Cough</official_title>
