  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is a randomised, double-blind, placebo-controlled, crossover, single centre study of
      gefapixant (AF-219/MK-7264) in subjects with idiopathic chronic cough designed to evaluate
      the effectiveness of gefapixant in reducing daytime objective cough frequency.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
